Package main

Class Team

java.lang.Object
main.Team
public class Team extends Object
The Team class describes a named team of 0-12 athletes It contains a static method for randomly generating a new team.
Version:
1.1, May 2023.
Author:
Lachlan Stewart and Stephen Hockey
